is designed to develop outstanding scholars for careers in research and teaching at leading business schools and universities throughout the world if you are looking for a place that will encourage you to inspire and to be inspired to challenge and to be challenged to discover the next great idea that will impact the world around you and to grow in meaningful ways we invite you to consider the phd program at the stanford graduate school of business admissions faculty & research alumni recruiters & companies giving executive education news about the gsb copyright 2012 stanford graduate school of business site help terms of use & policies stanford university
